{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "vulgate:numbers.12",
    "translationId": "vulgate",
    "bookSlug": "numbers",
    "chapterNumber": 12,
    "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12",
    "summary": "Source text for Numbers 12 in Clementine Vulgate."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.1",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:1",
      "text": "Locutaque est Maria et Aaron contra Moysen propter uxorem ejus Æthiopissam,",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.2",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:2",
      "text": "et dixerunt: Num per solum Moysen locutus est Dominus? nonne et nobis similiter est locutus? Quod cum audisset Dominus",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.3",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:3",
      "text": "(erat enim Moyses vir mitissimus super omnes homines qui morabantur in terra),",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.4",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:4",
      "text": "statim locutus est ad eum, et ad Aaron et Mariam: Egredimini vos tantum tres ad tabernaculum fœderis. Cumque fuissent egressi,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.5",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:5",
      "text": "descendit Dominus in columna nubis, et stetit in introitu tabernaculi, vocans Aaron et Mariam. Qui cum issent,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.6",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:6",
      "text": "dixit ad eos: Audite sermones meos: si quis fuerit inter vos propheta Domini, in visione apparebo ei, vel per somnium loquar ad illum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.7",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:7",
      "text": "At non talis servus meus Moyses, qui in omni domo mea fidelissimus est:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.8",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:8",
      "text": "ore enim ad os loquor ei: et palam, et non per ænigmata et figuras Dominum videt. Quare ergo non timuistis detrahere servo meo Moysi?",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.9",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:9",
      "text": "Iratusque contra eos, abiit:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.10",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:10",
      "text": "nubes quoque recessit quæ erat super tabernaculum: et ecce Maria apparuit candens lepra quasi nix. Cumque respexisset eam Aaron, et vidisset perfusam lepra,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.11",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:11",
      "text": "ait ad Moysen: Obsecro, domine mi, ne imponas nobis hoc peccatum quod stulte commisimus,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.12",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:12",
      "text": "ne fiat hæc quasi mortua, et ut abortivum quod projicitur de vulva matris suæ: ecce jam medium carnis ejus devoratum est a lepra.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.13",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:13",
      "text": "Clamavitque Moyses ad Dominum, dicens: Deus, obsecro, sana eam.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.14",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:14",
      "text": "Cui respondit Dominus: Si pater ejus spuisset in faciem illius, nonne debuerat saltem septem diebus rubore suffundi? separetur septem diebus extra castra, et postea revocabitur.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.12.15",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 12,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 12:15",
      "text": "Exclusa est itaque Maria extra castra septem diebus: et populus non est motus de loco illo, donec revocata est Maria.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
